I"<h3 id="문제">문제</h3>

<p>정수를 저장한 배열, arr 에서 가장 작은 수를 제거한 배열을 리턴하는 함수, solution을 완성해주세요. 단, 리턴하려는 배열이 빈 배열인 경우엔 배열에 -1을 채워 리턴하세요. 예를들어 arr이 [4,3,2,1]인 경우는 [4,3,2]를 리턴 하고, [10]면 [-1]을 리턴 합니다.</p>

<h3 id="풀이">풀이</h3>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">solution</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">arr</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">answer</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
    <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">arr</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="n">answer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">arr</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">remove</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">min</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">arr</span><span class="p">))</span>
        <span class="n">answer</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">arr</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">answer</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

